A cyberpunk cityscape at night where two massive server towers face each other across a neon-lit chasm, connected by streams of glowing encrypted data packets flowing between them like a digital bridge. The left tower pulses with electric blue energy representing a cloud platform, while the right tower glows with warm orange circuits. Between them, a single golden key-shaped beam of light cuts through the data streams, acting as a secure conduit. Rain falls through holographic advertisements, reflecting off wet streets far below. The scene is viewed from a dramatic low angle, emphasizing the towering scale of the infrastructure and the critical importance of the secure connection point.
